Hi PPL, like many of you I was stuck at 99.9% and I still only have that much, however I am able to watch entire film on DVD. I downloaded a free program called AVI Preview from   http://www.avipreview.com/download.htm   Open the 99.9% file in it and after full file has loaded in you should be able to watch whole thing. The second Icon in toolbar is the Save As icon, click this and save the movie as "whatever you want".avi    There you go. use your favourite DVD creating software and import this new avi and relive this old classic
